Interface HarvestSource

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BaseNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileHarvestSource, FileNode, FolderNode, ObjectFolderNode, RootNode

    public interface HarvestSource
    This interface is all that is needed by a harvester operation to describe a heirarchy (tree) of objects that are to be harvested.
